                     <h1>The situation is as follows:  <small>_____  intro</h1></small>
                       <p>A runaway consumer culture and obsession upon immediate gratification have left the public at large fixated with the acquisition of capital, material, and social standing. Rumors persist of a secret cabal of motivated and idealistic individuals who seek to loosen the grip of a consumerist ideology. You have received a cryptic piece of information from these rebels, calling themselves Project Mayhem, and have been seeking to join their ranks. That is, if they do in fact exist.</p>
                       <p> <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" role="button" id="toIntro1">Enter the fray</a></p>
                </div>
    
                <div id="intro1">
                   <p>After several weeks of following rumors to seemingly dead ends, you are contacted by an individual claiming to respresent Project Mayhem.</p>
    
                    <p>He wears nondescript black clothes and a hood that
conceals all but his face, and gives you a time and place to be in order to
begin your formal indoctrination. Once you confirm you understand your
instructions, he takes his leave.  </p>                     <br/>
<h2>*   *  *</h2>                     <br/>                     <p>At the
rendezvous, you see him waiting with an associate, both wearing black slacks and
t-shirts. Upon your arrival, they greet you aloofly, obviously sizing you up.
After a brief round of questioning, they announce you are free to coninue your
entry process, but in order to do so you must first agree to be drugged and
accompany them elsewhere.</p>                     <br>
    
                    <p>You are welcome to refuse, but if you do, Project Mayhem will be closed to you forever. This is your only chance.</p>
                     <br>
                     <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" role="button" id="toIntro2">Continue</a></p>
                     <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" role="button" id="bowOut">On second thought...</a></p>
                     </p>
