                </div>
                <div id="intro2">
                    <p>You agree, nervously. All manner of worst-case scenarios run through your mind, but you find your resolve.</p>

                    <p>They tell you the drug is a pschotomimetic, and it will make it almost impossible for you to form or maintain complicated lies, in the event you are a member of the State's Secret Police.</p>
                    <p>The plan is thus: they will effectively dose you, load you in a van heading for an undisclosed location, and question you further. If they are satisfied with your performance, you will become an initiated member of Project Mayhem, and then the real work will begin. </p>
                    <p>"Are you prepared?"</p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg toIntro3" role="button" id="toIntro3">Continue</a></p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg toIntro3" role="button" id="woah">"Wait, what did he just say?"</a></p>

                </div>
                <div id="intro3">
                    <p>Very suddenly, before you can tell what has happened, a spray bottle emerges in an agent's hand and is sprayed directly in to your face.</p>

                    <p>You curse, but not before you take a panicked breath of the narcotic. Things are already starting to get fuzzy. You try to steady yourself, coming to grips with the situation. The agents help you as your balance begins to falter.</p>

                    <p>They lead you gently to a van idling around the corner. Once all of you board into the back, the driver pulls out. You are already too disoriented to track where you are going. In the back of the van, the men ask you your name.</p>
